  ∃ (E : CPTPMap d₃ d₁) (D : CPTPMap d₂ d₄), D.compose (Λ₁.compose E) = Λ₂

/--
A channel A `εApproximates` channel B (of the same dimensions) if the for every state ρ, the fidelity F(A(ρ), B(ρ)) is at least 1-ε.
-/
